32:29.556 --> 32:32.472
Dean's bringing them
home tonight.

32:32.515 --> 32:36.041
- That's good.

32:36.084 --> 32:38.130
- And I have your cut.

32:38.173 --> 32:40.871
- Even better.

32:46.399 --> 32:49.663
- I don't have it here.

32:59.542 --> 33:01.414
Sorry.

33:01.457 --> 33:04.634
Didn't get a chance to...

33:06.941 --> 33:09.161
Can I get you
something to eat?

33:09.204 --> 33:12.381
- Yeah, what you got?

33:16.646 --> 33:18.735
- I could make you a sandwich.

33:18.779 --> 33:22.609
- Yeah, I'm not really much
of a sandwich guy.

33:24.350 --> 33:26.526
- I'm out of bread anyway.

33:26.569 --> 33:29.137
- [chuckles]

33:30.486 --> 33:33.054
What am I doing here,
Elizabeth?

33:52.247 --> 33:54.119
- It's just habit.

35:40.225 --> 35:43.271
[both breathing heavily]

35:52.062 --> 35:53.890
- [moans softly]

35:55.414 --> 35:55.631
.

35:55.675 --> 35:59.026
- My kids will be home soon.

36:02.160 --> 36:04.249
Here's your cut.

36:04.292 --> 36:07.643
- I thought you left it
at home?

36:07.687 --> 36:08.818
- Guess not.

36:08.862 --> 36:10.864
- [chuckles]

36:10.907 --> 36:12.387
All right, swing by tomorrow.

36:12.431 --> 36:13.954
I'll hook you up
with the funny money.

36:13.997 --> 36:15.216
- I don't need it.

36:15.260 --> 36:18.176
- Yeah, but how you--
- I'm not.

36:21.004 --> 36:23.659
I'm done.

36:25.748 --> 36:28.273
- Is that right?

36:28.316 --> 36:31.189
- No more cash,
no more pills.

36:36.629 --> 36:39.762
I'm gonna take a shower.
You should go.

36:41.373 --> 36:43.679
It's over.

36:45.942 --> 36:47.422
- Next?

36:48.293 --> 36:51.557
[keyboard clacking]

36:55.343 --> 36:57.345
Welcome to Qwik Cash.

36:57.389 --> 36:59.391
How may I assist you today?

36:59.434 --> 37:01.175
- Why didn't you tell the cops?

37:01.219 --> 37:03.438
- We offer many different types
of loans.

37:03.482 --> 37:06.311
- I know when
I'm being hustled.

37:06.354 --> 37:09.227
- Did you mother teach you
those manners?

37:09.270 --> 37:11.881
How 'bout a "thank you"?

37:11.925 --> 37:13.579
- If you want a cut
of the money,

37:13.622 --> 37:14.928
it's already gone.

37:14.971 --> 37:18.279
- Yeah, I didn't think it went
into your 401K.

37:18.323 --> 37:20.281
- Okay, you know what?

37:20.325 --> 37:22.196
You might think I'm trash,

37:22.240 --> 37:24.416
but I work really hard
for what I have.

37:24.459 --> 37:26.853
And I've got a 12-hour shift
ahead of me--

37:26.896 --> 37:28.289
my second double of the week--

37:28.333 --> 37:30.335
and it's barely gonna cover
my groceries

37:30.378 --> 37:31.988
let alone the roof
over my head--

37:32.032 --> 37:33.512
which I only have, by the way,

37:33.555 --> 37:36.341
because my mother--
who wrote the book on manners,

37:36.384 --> 37:39.518
I'll have you know--died.

37:39.561 --> 37:42.651
God rest her soul.

37:43.826 --> 37:45.001
- I want your address.

37:45.045 --> 37:46.394
- Don't you have it
in your system?

37:46.438 --> 37:49.702
- No, I need it
for your school district.

37:49.745 --> 37:51.181
- You can get your GED online.

37:51.225 --> 37:53.532
- I majored in finance
at MSU, bitch.

37:53.575 --> 37:56.186
- Then who's it for?

37:56.230 --> 37:59.233
- My nephew.

37:59.277 --> 38:01.888
He's smart.

38:01.931 --> 38:05.283
Or I--I could go to the cops.

38:06.458 --> 38:08.286
- Fine.

38:10.244 --> 38:12.115
- Little nerd just needs
a leg up.

38:12.159 --> 38:14.335
- We all do.

38:14.379 --> 38:17.338
[women vocalizing]

38:17.382 --> 38:19.645
[bittersweet music]

38:19.688 --> 38:23.866
♪ Save it for the sake
of the fight ♪

38:23.910 --> 38:25.868
♪

38:25.912 --> 38:31.483
♪ Copy/paste
the child inside ♪

38:31.526 --> 38:37.532
♪ You used to smile,
but now you are staged ♪

