through speakers]

39:58.439 --> 40:00.049
[billiard balls thudding]

40:00.093 --> 40:01.442
- Hey.

40:01.486 --> 40:03.009
- Hey.
- Hi.

40:03.052 --> 40:04.619
- Noah, right?
It's Noah?

40:04.663 --> 40:06.055
both: Yeah.
- Oops.

40:06.099 --> 40:07.143
- Mm-hmm.

40:07.187 --> 40:08.841
- Um, so I had an epiphany.

40:08.884 --> 40:12.192
Why are we, as a company, not
making, uh,

40:12.235 --> 40:15.500
bite-sized... treats?

40:15.543 --> 40:17.806
- I think we should
slow things down.

40:17.850 --> 40:20.853
With us.

40:20.896 --> 40:21.897
- Oh.

40:21.941 --> 40:24.030
- Yeah, I just...

40:24.073 --> 40:26.032
you know, I have--
I have a kid,

40:26.075 --> 40:28.382
so I--I gotta be careful.

40:28.426 --> 40:30.471
You know?
- Yeah, right.

40:30.515 --> 40:33.953
- I don't even really know
anything about you, you know?

40:33.996 --> 40:35.955
- What do you want to know?

40:35.998 --> 40:37.522
- Just that...

40:37.565 --> 40:40.438
you're not a total D-bag.

40:40.481 --> 40:46.182
♪

40:46.226 --> 40:49.229
- [mumbles indistinctly]

40:49.272 --> 40:51.884
Here's the thing...

40:51.927 --> 40:54.016
uh, I kinda am.

40:54.060 --> 40:55.975
- Seriously?

40:56.018 --> 40:57.324
- Yeah, I'm so sorry.

40:57.367 --> 40:58.412
- Oh, my God.

40:58.456 --> 41:01.241
What--why do I always do this?

41:01.284 --> 41:04.026
- I'm not just a...

41:04.070 --> 41:06.768
grocery store manager.

41:06.812 --> 41:09.379
♪

41:09.423 --> 41:11.512
I'm...

41:14.123 --> 41:15.734
I'm...

41:15.777 --> 41:18.693
on probation.

41:21.348 --> 41:22.610
- For what?

41:22.654 --> 41:24.917
- Well, I stole
from my last job,

41:24.960 --> 41:28.529
and then I had to lie
to get this one.

41:28.573 --> 41:30.749
- What did you steal?

41:30.792 --> 41:31.924
- Money.

41:31.967 --> 41:33.578
Lots of it over
a long period of time

41:33.621 --> 41:35.667
and then, uh--
I mean, it was, uh--

41:35.710 --> 41:38.060
they didn't notice at first
and then it got easier.

41:38.104 --> 41:41.455
Listen, I'm not--this is not
something I'm proud of.

41:41.499 --> 41:44.284
- [laughs]
Noah.

41:44.327 --> 41:48.201
- What?
- Sweet, sweet Noah.

41:48.244 --> 41:49.681
[inhales]

41:49.724 --> 41:50.725
- What?

41:50.769 --> 41:52.858
- Okay, we're gonna need
some shots

41:52.901 --> 41:54.076
for this conversation,

41:54.120 --> 41:56.601
because we are
so much more alike

41:56.644 --> 41:58.603
then you could ever know.

